{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I used to be a Malthusian."},{"time":3000,"text":"This was my mental model of the world:"},{"time":6000,"text":"exploding population, small planet;"},{"time":9000,"text":"it's going to lead to ugly things."},{"time":11000,"text":"But I'm moving past Malthus,"},{"time":13000,"text":"because I think that we just might be about 150 years"},{"time":16000,"text":"from a kind of new enlightenment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18000,"text":"Here's why."},{"time":20000,"text":"This is the U.N.'s population data,"},{"time":22000,"text":"you may have seen, for the world."},{"time":25000,"text":"And the world's population expected to top out"},{"time":27000,"text":"at something hopefully a bit less than 10 billion, late this century."},{"time":31000,"text":"And after that, most likely it's going to begin to decline."},{"time":35000,"text":"So what then?"},{"time":38000,"text":"Most of the economic models are built around scarcity and growth."},{"time":41000,"text":"So a lot of economists"},{"time":43000,"text":"look at declining population"},{"time":45000,"text":"and expect to see stagnation, maybe depression."},{"time":48000,"text":"But a declining population is going to have"},{"time":51000,"text":"at least two very beneficial economic effects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"One: fewer people on a fixed amount of land"},{"time":60000,"text":"make investing in property a bad bet."},{"time":64000,"text":"In the cities, a lot of the cost of property"},{"time":68000,"text":"is actually wrapped up in its speculative value."},{"time":72000,"text":"Take away land speculation,"},{"time":74000,"text":"price of land drops."},{"time":76000,"text":"And that begins to lift a heavy burden"},{"time":78000,"text":"off the world's poor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81000,"text":"Number two: a declining population"},{"time":85000,"text":"means scarce labor."},{"time":87000,"text":"Scarce labor drives wages."},{"time":89000,"text":"As wages increase"},{"time":91000,"text":"that also lifts the burden on the poor and the working class."},{"time":96000,"text":"Now I'm not talking about a radical drop in population like we saw in the Black Death."},{"time":100000,"text":"But look what happened in Europe"},{"time":102000,"text":"after the plague:"},{"time":104000,"text":"rising wages,"},{"time":106000,"text":"land reform,"},{"time":108000,"text":"technological innovation,"},{"time":111000,"text":"birth of the middle class;"},{"time":113000,"text":"and after that, forward-looking social movements"},{"time":117000,"text":"like the Renaissance,"},{"time":119000,"text":"and later the Enlightenment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"Most of our cultural heritage has tended to look backward,"},{"time":125000,"text":"romanticizing the past."},{"time":128000,"text":"All of the Western religions begin with the notion of Eden,"},{"time":131000,"text":"and descend through a kind of profligate present"},{"time":134000,"text":"to a very ugly future."},{"time":137000,"text":"So human history is viewed"},{"time":139000,"text":"as sort of this downhill slide"},{"time":141000,"text":"from the good old days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143000,"text":"But I think we're in for another change,"},{"time":146000,"text":"about two generations after the top of that curve,"},{"time":149000,"text":"once the effects of a declining population"},{"time":152000,"text":"start to settle in."},{"time":154000,"text":"At that point, we'll start romanticizing the future again,"},{"time":158000,"text":"instead of the nasty, brutish past."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161000,"text":"So why does this matter?"},{"time":163000,"text":"Why talk about social-economic movements"},{"time":165000,"text":"that may be more than a century away?"},{"time":167000,"text":"Because transitions are dangerous times."},{"time":171000,"text":"When land owners start to lose money,"},{"time":174000,"text":"and labor demands more pay,"},{"time":176000,"text":"there are some powerful interests that are going to fear for the future."},{"time":180000,"text":"Fear for the future leads to some rash decisions."},{"time":184000,"text":"If we have a positive view about the future"},{"time":187000,"text":"then we may be able to accelerate through that turn,"},{"time":190000,"text":"instead of careening off a cliff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"If we can make it through the next 150 years,"},{"time":196000,"text":"I think that your great great grandchildren"},{"time":198000,"text":"will forget all about Malthus."},{"time":200000,"text":"And instead, they'll be planning for the future"},{"time":204000,"text":"and starting to build the 22nd Century Enlightenment."},{"time":207000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":209000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}